  "description": "<div id=\"product-detail\">\n<h4>Application:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>BMW 335i / 335xi (E90/E91/E92/E93) N54B30 3.0L Turbocharged, 2007 - 2010</li>\n<li>BMW 335is (E92/E93) N54B30 3.0L Turbocharged, 2011 - 2013</li>\n</ul>\n<p style=\"color: #800000;\"><strong>Will NOT fit 135i, 535i, Z4, X6, 740i</strong></p>\n<h4>Features:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>OE design, the turbos handle max power 500HP.</li>\n<li>High-quality replacements for factory parts. Excellent durability and optimized vehicle performance.</li>\n<li>Direct replacement for factory turbo parts.</li>\n<li>Center rotating bearing housing designed to work with factory oil and coolant lines.</li>\n<li>Component balanced using state-of-the-art VSR high-speed balancing machine, avg 0.5 mg or less.</li>\n<li>Accessories shown in photos are included.</li>\n<li>1-year warranty for any manufacturing defect.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Technical Specifications:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Durable Compressor Wheel: 12(6+6) blades, Size: 35.7*46 mm</li>\n<li>Turbine Wheel: 11 blades, Size: 35.2*40 mm</li>\n<li style=\"color: #f37934;\">We also sell 17T and 19T N54 Twin Turbos. Please contact us if interested.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Turbo Part Number:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>49131-07000, 49131-07001, 49131-07006, 49131-07007, 49131-07010</li>\n<li>49131-07011, 49131-07015, 49131-07016, 49131-07107, 49131-07018</li>\n<li>49131-07019, 49131-07030, 49131-07031, 49131-07040, 49131-07041</li>\n<li>49131-07065, 49131-07066, 49131-07067, 49131-07068, 49131-07069</li>\n<li>49131-07075, 49131-07076, 49131-07077, 49131-07078, 49131-07079</li>\n<li>49131-07161, 49131-07170, 49131-07180, 49131-07205, 49131-07206</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>O.E.M Number:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>11654564711, 11654564710, 11657563685, 11657563686, 11657583863</li>\n<li>11657583864, 11657593015, 11657593016, 11657649289, 11657649290</li>\n<li>4564710, 4564711, 7583863, 7583864, 7593015</li>\n<li>7593016, 7563685, 7563686, 7649289, 7649290</li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
